#

French Bistro Burger Delight

$25
850 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Contains DairyHigh Protein

Tags:

GourmetComfort FoodFrench Inspired

Description

A juicy beef burger infused with herb garlic butter and topped with melted Gruyère cheese, accompanied by crispy truffle fries and a refreshing mixed greens salad.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef: 1 lb
  • Gruyère Cheese: 4 slices
  • Burger Buns: 4
  • Herb Garlic Butter: 1/2 cup
  • Truffle Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Potatoes (for fries): 2 large
  • Mixed Greens: 4 cups
  • Dijon Mustard: 2 tbsp
  • Olive Oil: 3 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
